{"tid":403132,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人早晚都洗頭？","createTime":"2017-09-17T03:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T03:36:16.000Z","uid":64005,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"368a29f8c0331dbd2957c4ffce1de4f522958c78","tid":403132,"uid":64005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"驚唔驚甩頭髮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a316ddc515429859cee2748bfd679039a00dda","tid":403132,"uid":30249,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:21:49.000Z","msg":"早晚洗一次 髮線向後移<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唉</span></span>"},{"pid":"0806c8564aaf743f59a58a81479d3479aeb1a038","tid":403132,"uid":146031,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:38:03.000Z","msg":"洗左三四年<br />\n無甩 仲長得好撚快 三個星期要剪一次頭"},{"pid":"7a3b619481747878b429396e63fdeb71055adeae","tid":403132,"uid":106326,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:44:26.000Z","msg":"唔洗頭會死<br />\n<br />\n好少甩頭髮，同樣生得好快。<br />\n<br />\n其實你驚既咪唔好用洗頭水，或者轉用手工肥皂。<br />\n<br />\n我朝頭早會認真啲洗，因為要吹頭返工。<br />\n<br />\n夜晚反正都係訓教會亂晒，純粹洗乾淨就算。"},{"pid":"e64a3ffb318a13a8136c8a71244e42dddd60a7fa","tid":403132,"uid":104793,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗頭會死<br />\n<br />\n好少甩頭髮，同樣生得好快。<br />\n<br />\n其實你驚既咪唔好用洗頭水，或者轉用手工肥皂。<br />\n<br />\n我朝頭早會認真啲洗，因為要吹頭返工。<br />\n<br />\n夜晚反正都係訓教會亂晒，純粹洗乾淨就算。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我相反，夜晚唔想頭髮污糟訓落枕頭，會洗乾淨啲。朝早頭髮亂晒同時又趕住出門口洗一洗濕完就吹乾方便造型"},{"pid":"46057bfc0ff49f7173df0e52d6991cef76ebbb56","tid":403132,"uid":103380,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗左三四年<br />\n無甩 仲長得好撚快 三個星期要剪一次頭</blockquote><br />\n巴打我同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗會好痕同好多頭皮 洗完會舒服成日<br />\n唔洗就會唔舒服成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c2ab91437afe7ce21960e18a5fc9454f8e4285","tid":403132,"uid":1403,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"淨係朝早先洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚晚返到屋企幾大汗都廢事洗完又吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedcfe583ad2261d0dd1c152b293b698c08cce35","tid":403132,"uid":26014,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"我覺得洗得多先唔會甩頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc4f8a297523aed47831ee32d0e24912bc1d014","tid":403132,"uid":64005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗左三四年<br />\n無甩 仲長得好撚快 三個星期要剪一次頭</blockquote><br />\n巴打我同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗會好痕同好多頭皮 洗完會舒服成日<br />\n唔洗就會唔舒服成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但中學開始咁做 維持左7/8年<br />\n髮線愈黎愈後 不過一開始嚴重d <br />\n唔知係咪洗頭水/護髮素洗唔哂<br />\n近年用天然果d洗頭水感覺好似好d<br />\n不過都救唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前額甩哂"},{"pid":"47ae5cf974d541892207bd31bbf69b1fffc4217a","tid":403132,"uid":104658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:27:24.000Z","msg":"早同臨瞓前洗都唔好   好似係血氣問題<br />\n<br />\n均衡飲食  食得健康點洗都唔甩"},{"pid":"93d8990868b330f5da25c1f23fd12fb4b45ff460","tid":403132,"uid":100760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"朝早開花灑純清水洗頭，純粹為左髮型<br />\n夜晚先用洗頭水，為清潔"},{"pid":"67e48bb032e229a9e2187320dcd5cd985d9e4b91","tid":403132,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朝早開花灑純清水洗頭，純粹為左髮型<br />\n夜晚先用洗頭水，為清潔</blockquote><br />\n你地就好，我個頭好亂唔落洗頭水同護髮素洗軟返啲頭髮係造唔到型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人用開texture maker ，有冇介紹"},{"pid":"4913a373481780cbf68e8d0daca77952380ae348","tid":403132,"uid":8795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:59:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係朝早先洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚晚返到屋企幾大汗都廢事洗完又吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0835e21810cbf5289d967e24f527dbb033017178","tid":403132,"uid":24021,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:06:19.000Z","msg":"早晚都要洗<br />\n唔洗嗰日個人都頹啲"},{"pid":"6d8641405dfa305e054c31d1a060a6d1efc16e21","tid":403132,"uid":24021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗左三四年<br />\n無甩 仲長得好撚快 三個星期要剪一次頭</blockquote><br />\n巴打我同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗會好痕同好多頭皮 洗完會舒服成日<br />\n唔洗就會唔舒服成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但中學開始咁做 維持左7/8年<br />\n髮線愈黎愈後 不過一開始嚴重d <br />\n唔知係咪洗頭水/護髮素洗唔哂<br />\n近年用天然果d洗頭水感覺好似好d<br />\n不過都救唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前額甩哂</blockquote><br />\n真係關早晚洗頭事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都差唔多早晚洗頭7/8年 無咁既問題喎<br />\n<br />\n問題反而係慣咗之後如果無得洗個頭會痕到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使無出過汗"},{"pid":"df5751d4d7129f5cf148b2553258b3c0feaedef1","tid":403132,"uid":58140,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:09:59.000Z","msg":"起身洗頭+沖涼+洗面+刷牙<br />\n返到屋企沖涼+洗頭<br />\n訓之前用暖水沖沖個身訓教<br />\n呢個習慣由我小學6年級到宜家都係咁"},{"pid":"0fd5e2b7968dc2ee2d4c73729624dfae08f2daad","tid":403132,"uid":129039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:10:52.000Z","msg":"我家姐 一個禮拜都唔洗一次頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fbcb5ac0e3477e1c975b1a7aeab2110dffb104","tid":403132,"uid":74824,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朝早唔洗個頭又油又臭<br />\n夜晚唔洗又污染我張床"},{"pid":"da95ded830150146ebf455759cecafc8828e43e1","tid":403132,"uid":55213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:37:26.000Z","msg":"早晚都洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗左5-6年"},{"pid":"c62b6ba3c75001090d8ce5491604c2085da81b30","tid":403132,"uid":4417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗左三四年<br />\n無甩 仲長得好撚快 三個星期要剪一次頭</blockquote><br />\n巴打我同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗會好痕同好多頭皮 洗完會舒服成日<br />\n唔洗就會唔舒服成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但中學開始咁做 維持左7/8年<br />\n髮線愈黎愈後 不過一開始嚴重d <br />\n唔知係咪洗頭水/護髮素洗唔哂<br />\n近年用天然果d洗頭水感覺好似好d<br />\n不過都救唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前額甩哂</blockquote><br />\n求洗頭水推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368e345a6c51f1ac1957d37c8a893ee932f0e9fd","tid":403132,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"太油，唔洗唔得"},{"pid":"802b24f5adccb011c2bbdde306663018ad08a90e","tid":403132,"uid":95033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得早晚洗頭冇太大問題，落唔落洗頭水都冇太大問題。<br />\n反而長期用護髮素加上洗唔乾淨先會甩頭髮。<br />\n利申聽髮型師講既"},{"pid":"d0a7c859130f3d90906269288a342b0f472bd72c","tid":403132,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:19:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗左三四年<br />\n無甩 仲長得好撚快 三個星期要剪一次頭</blockquote><br />\n巴打我同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗會好痕同好多頭皮 洗完會舒服成日<br />\n唔洗就會唔舒服成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但中學開始咁做 維持左7/8年<br />\n髮線愈黎愈後 不過一開始嚴重d <br />\n唔知係咪洗頭水/護髮素洗唔哂<br />\n近年用天然果d洗頭水感覺好似好d<br />\n不過都救唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前額甩哂</blockquote><br />\n真係關早晚洗頭事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都差唔多早晚洗頭7/8年 無咁既問題喎<br />\n<br />\n問題反而係慣咗之後如果無得洗個頭會痕到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使無出過汗</blockquote><br />\n屌 同你一樣<br />\n巴打係咪都係個頭好撚厚<br />\n<br />\n我剪頭髮一定要偷薄 洗完都好易乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a69112108ff4035128e078cc49d074d966d18f","tid":403132,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:52:25.000Z","msg":"早晚一定會洗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9868d20a1a209b7a1834bba40ee367ab24412c8a","tid":403132,"uid":72979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔洗頭會死<br />\n<br />\n好少甩頭髮，同樣生得好快。<br />\n<br />\n其實你驚既咪唔好用洗頭水，或者轉用手工肥皂。<br />\n<br />\n我朝頭早會認真啲洗，因為要吹頭返工。<br />\n<br />\n夜晚反正都係訓教會亂晒，純粹洗乾淨就算。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我相反，夜晚唔想頭髮污糟訓落枕頭，會洗乾淨啲。朝早頭髮亂晒同時又趕住出門口洗一洗濕完就吹乾方便造型</blockquote><br />\n我都係夜晚唔想整污糟個枕頭 點都會洗乾淨<br />\n日頭就是但洗下 吹番就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19ff6c25f3dbb5c2f1f338122acf5f39071d9b5","tid":403132,"uid":88394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"洗完一次個頭都仲有油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 要連續洗兩次; 夜晚沖涼再洗多次"},{"pid":"781d87d765df9372076dec3d8dad21a0690d8f22","tid":403132,"uid":64005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"個枕頭幾日就有勁多頭皮 唔知正唔正常"},{"pid":"8ffad9c6c71928da90ae87f194f12d71f7da2d30","tid":403132,"uid":52571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:30:07.000Z","msg":"早晚洗乜唔係正常咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朝早要返工<br />\n夜晚返左成日工 個頭好污糟多塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ce29337e8bfa8094ef70cf5d6e0fcc83ca4a90","tid":403132,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:32:06.000Z","msg":"早上都一定要洗啦,<br />\n唔洗連埋啲頭油gel 埋一齊,<br />\n到中午勁撚頭㾗,<br />\n又笠,<br />\n<br />\n訓一晚啲頭油都出晒黎"},{"pid":"03afc2faa8404a4556e304fc37d50647a55b3e46","tid":403132,"uid":18704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早晚都要洗<br />\n唔洗嗰日個人都頹啲</blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad25447e00f8d3ef5bce46d781736b12ea6633c5","tid":403132,"uid":24021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗左三四年<br />\n無甩 仲長得好撚快 三個星期要剪一次頭</blockquote><br />\n巴打我同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗會好痕同好多頭皮 洗完會舒服成日<br />\n唔洗就會唔舒服成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但中學開始咁做 維持左7/8年<br />\n髮線愈黎愈後 不過一開始嚴重d <br />\n唔知係咪洗頭水/護髮素洗唔哂<br />\n近年用天然果d洗頭水感覺好似好d<br />\n不過都救唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前額甩哂</blockquote><br />\n真係關早晚洗頭事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都差唔多早晚洗頭7/8年 無咁既問題喎<br />\n<br />\n問題反而係慣咗之後如果無得洗個頭會痕到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使無出過汗</blockquote><br />\n屌 同你一樣<br />\n巴打係咪都係個頭好撚厚<br />\n<br />\n我剪頭髮一定要偷薄 洗完都好易乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個頭係厚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁多頭髮"},{"pid":"0116b72aac86e5d66fcd640b81a5a6e47d76c6e2","tid":403132,"uid":141529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:50:50.000Z","msg":"日日朝早都實洗頭 唔洗唔舒服<br />\n夜晚淨係用水沖下就算<br />\n慣左5年 未有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff3ef9c420f048497c0fdddc7a9f99da0af19fc","tid":403132,"uid":3602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:13:58.000Z","msg":"for sure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3ea703cc74217d00d7fae457e5e8ed1b2e1266","tid":403132,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:18:18.000Z","msg":"gel 頭前一定要洗。。訓前落gel又要洗"},{"pid":"d6a3af80ecfb8658356634e054e2e4fe3d73c190","tid":403132,"uid":16007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:23:49.000Z","msg":"朝早起身洗一洗吹完落gel效果都好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5861ae742fe56519e52f41e4a4c9d778a85416","tid":403132,"uid":39685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:37:50.000Z","msg":"早晚洗 洗左廿年 洗走D油好gel D<br />\n頭髮長得好快，冇甩頭髮既情況出現"},{"pid":"08a92795e2f45efe2a88cd3f2d8164fe7e9744d6","tid":403132,"uid":15558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:47:58.000Z","msg":"日日gel頭表示未撚驚過 呢一年都係all back<br />\n<br />\n因為gel頭關係朝朝一定要洗一次頭 有時一日洗三次頭<br />\n<br />\n24歲仔仲係好濃密同埋長得幾快"},{"pid":"479b661031b1deb265be5c7537666bc6c3debac4","tid":403132,"uid":136618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:51:18.000Z","msg":"一時時啦<br />\n如果朝早要gel頭就點都會洗，其實我估好多男人起身都會洗頭，因爲一起身個頭真係好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f413d8c7accf4c9730981cc09eb3749737031434","tid":403132,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:53:37.000Z","msg":"由細到大都係早晚洗頭沖涼 就算好凍都係 <br />\n朝早多數洗得乾淨啲 夜晚就求其啲<br />\n冇髮線後移 把頭髮仲好厚 一個月剪一兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9629a5c6e1ee3016c12b2ed9e9ff55f90a74d2","tid":403132,"uid":92694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:55:51.000Z","msg":"淨係晚先洗<br />\n但甩勁多頭髮，成張床，地下，成屋都頭髮<br />\n但甩極個頭仲好厚，好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e668fe2142ebaeebd3280ff797f46c6756136958","tid":403132,"uid":119008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:58:30.000Z","msg":"早晚都洗<br />\n頭髮勁多勁厚<br />\n一長就會開始多頭皮<br />\n點算好"},{"pid":"f7cdaafce56832774682c34d5f3829410fb96b45","tid":403132,"uid":31354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:15:20.000Z","msg":"朝早訓到飛起哂唔洗唔得, 又油, 個頭又長得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3c5b9608a362bb4832d6fe05efaab806072326","tid":403132,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:18:39.000Z","msg":"樓主你老豆有冇甩 我早晚但冇野 你九成九係遺傳"},{"pid":"de94b7805bbd0b917a8496753e644cd475c50146","tid":403132,"uid":49269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:34:27.000Z","msg":"唔洗番工既日子<br />\n一日三四次以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一樣濃密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4df63a4750747d50d512ec22d98ae24668b6238","tid":403132,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:38:32.000Z","msg":"一日沖三次涼 平時訓醒成身汗一次 放學返黎成身汗一次 夜晚訓前再一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3d11a6b09906bbf48d0a22415675d9604222cc","tid":403132,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"由中學洗到大學 一樣係咁多頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個零月就要剪一次"},{"pid":"dbd6fb2f36e5f676d8fd3f3d6812713e197a9b80","tid":403132,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T03:16:24.000Z","msg":"小學果陣好多頭皮<br />\n中學開始早晚都洗就冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔早晚洗頭慘過冇得訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d9f09d938e3c5817be810c2f49fa0e368dd88b","tid":403132,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T03:17:11.000Z","msg":"要gel頭 早晚洗一係基本"},{"pid":"8434f47625985ba7a5216752adb437542b2797ca","tid":403132,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T03:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n持續咁好多年喇喎"},{"pid":"ac93d5a45ccfd509a427f03a3db6891a5ce290a7","tid":403132,"uid":132185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T03:19:41.000Z","msg":"早晩都洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗左6年幾，無問題 朝早起身洗個頭人都精神啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa8b2ccfcdd5d9b24afe3da4dad3055b5f0533c","tid":403132,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T04:34:53.000Z","msg":"講到尾甩頭髮都係睇自己體質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過之前有段時間都有留意下，發覺唔知係咪果段時間太留意，好似甩特別多咁，勁介意勁勁連梳頭都唔敢，後尾無理之後過一排無再特別留意之後又覺得無乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完全係自己心理作用。果排仲上網查左話咩正常每人每日都會甩50條頭髮，又話咩訓醒起身睇下枕頭上面有幾多條頭髮跟住乘4定唔知5就係你今日會甩既數量"},{"pid":"add0857f627a718330782250915455cbae7d0921","tid":403132,"uid":131222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"朝早會就咁用水洗 方便gel頭<br />\n夜晚就一定落洗頭水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b740ac5a421fe5acea85d0c6254489e35943123e","tid":403132,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T21:45:56.000Z","msg":"斷好多頭髮<br />\n啲頭髮仲好似線頭咁"},{"pid":"8426f2bf218df43d3bb03f276f78f7ee6f7cebdd","tid":403132,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T21:51:08.000Z","msg":"但我洗咁多頭<br />\n個頭成日好痕"},{"pid":"e60bb6cad0a58893e5610009138278105acd334e","tid":403132,"uid":63164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T22:32:08.000Z","msg":"我朝早一定要洗<br />\n唔洗既話出街個頭會勁油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436d3afa3ea368e7805e288b599c8adc33802fdb","tid":403132,"uid":33037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"洗得多唔會直接令你甩多左頭髮<br />\n可能係你用緊既洗頭水唔適合你<br />\n或者刺激性太高或者過敏<br />\n可以試下轉用天然成份既洗頭水或者洗髮皂<br />\n同埋髮囊積聚油脂污垢都會甩多啲頭髮<br />\n保持清潔衛生最緊要<br />\n所以早晚洗都好正常"},{"pid":"a92b71ed66c28a1af804a2e952884ae819f95629","tid":403132,"uid":143173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"淨係夜晚先洗"},{"pid":"250810fe06763edae5c11c752c4386b4dbcadf19","tid":403132,"uid":42624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:25:28.000Z","msg":"早晚都洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc4718cc0c390c701777f1ac9c0e3b100319327","tid":403132,"uid":37753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim